<variable name="code">

Solve the following simultaneous equations:

\[ 3x + y = 11 \] (1)

\[\frac{2x}{3} + \frac{2y}{3} = 8\] (2)

Euler's equation \( e^{i\pi}+1=0 \) is a beautiful equation.

