<box type="important">

If your equation requires special Nunjucks tags like {% raw %}`{{`{% endraw %} or {% raw %}`}}`{% endraw %},use a
[raw-endraw block together with v-pre](https://markbind.org/userGuide/tipsAndTricks.html#using-raw-endraw-to-display-content):

```markdown
{% raw %}{% raw %}\(e^{{\frac{1}{3}} + 1}\) {v-pre}{% endraw %}{% endraw %}
```

</box>

